oline%20supply%20and%20cause%20the%20national%20average%20gasoline%20price%20to%20dip%20below%20%243.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFalling%20prices%20at%20the%20gas%20pump%20would%20be%20welcome%20news%20for%20American%20drivers%20as%20they%20head%20into%20the%20summer%20vacation%20season%E2%80%94and%20what's%20good%20news%20for%20the%20consumer%20is%20good%20news%20for%20the%20economy.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%20estimates%20that%20roughly%2080%25%20of%20consumer%20savings%20from%20lower%20gas%20prices%20are%20spent%20elsewhere%2C%20and%20that%20a%20dollar%20swing%20in%20gas%20prices%20can%20translate%20into%20tens%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20of%20consumer%20firepower%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222df905af-decd-4e9a-8fc0-a12406dc8cfa%5C%22%3EOPEC%20to%20unleash%20supply%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMonday's%20price%20decline%20came%20after%20a%20weekend%20OPEC%2B%20meeting%2C%20in%20which%20the%20group%20of%208%20oil-producing%20countries%20said%20they%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-crash-trump-tariffs-opec-production-recession-trade-war-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincrease%20the%20supply%20of%20oil%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20month%20of%20June%20by%20411%2C000%20barrels%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20increasing%20supply%20of%20oil%20set%20to%20hit%20the%20market%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20demand%20is%20expected%20to%20weaken%20due%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Frecession%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20slowing%20global%20economy%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggesting%20that%20oil%20prices%20can%20keep%20falling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20solution%20to%20low%20prices%20is%20low%20prices%2C%26quot%3B%20Rob%20Thummel%2C%20senior%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20Tortoise%20Capital%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThummel%20said%20he%20expects%20oil%20prices%20could%20fall%20to%20the%20low%20%2450s%20per%20barrel%20in%20the%20short%20term%2C%20befor