C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20published%20a%20letter%20to%20OpenAI's%20website%20about%20the%20company's%20future%20structure%20on%20May%205%2C%202025.%3Cp%3EJason%20Redmond%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhistory-of-openai-company-chatgpt-elon-musk-founded-2022-12%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20its%20nonprofit%20will%20remain%20in%20control.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20transforming%20its%20structure%20as%20it%20looks%20to%20position%20itself%20to%20raise%20more%20money%20to%20train%20its%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECEO%20Sam%20Altman%20published%20a%20letter%20announcing%20the%20changes%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20appears%20to%20have%20decided%20that%20transferring%20control%20away%20from%20its%20nonprofit%20isn't%20worth%20the%20hassle%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20giant%20on%20Monday%20announced%20that%20its%20nonprofit%20would%20remain%20in%20control%20of%20its%20for-profit%20division%2C%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20its%20money-making%20chatbot%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20products%2C%20even%20after%20the%20subsidiary%20transforms%20into%20a%20public%20benefit%20corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20made%20the%20decision%20for%20the%20nonprofit%20to%20retain%20control%20of%20OpenAI%20after%20hearing%20from%20civic%20leaders%20and%20engaging%20in%20constructive%20dialogue%20with%20the%20offices%20of%20the%20Attorney%20General%20of%20Delaware%20and%20the%20Attorney%20General%20of%20California%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20wrote%20in%20a%20blog%20post%20published%20to%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-one-step-closer-becoming-profit-company-report-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20started%20nearly%20a%20decade%20ago%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20nonprofit%20research%20organization%20focused%20on%20the%20safe%20development%20of%20AI.%20In%202019%2C%20it%20added%20a%20for-profit%20arm%2C%20governed%20by%20its%20non-profit%2C%20to%20help%20raise%20funds%20for%20its%20mission.%20In%20September%2C%20the%20company%20officially%20announced%20it%20planned%20to%20move%20to%20a%20for-profit%20business%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-chatgpt-openai-ceo-career-net-worth-ycombinator-prepper-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECEO%20Sam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20published%20a%20letter%20he%20sent%20to%20OpenAI%20employees%20discussing%20the%20changes%2C%20which%20you%20can%20read%20in%20full%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223619ce1f-0b70-43bb-8160-7cc46c8cf2b4%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman's%20letter%20to%20employees%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOpenAI%20is%20not%20a%20normal%20company%20and%20never%20will%20be.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOur%20mission%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%20(AGI)%20benefits%20all%20of%20humanity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWhen%20we%20started%20OpenAI%2C%20we%20did%20not%20have%20a%20detailed%20sense%20for%20how%20we%20were%20going%20to%20accomplish%20our%20mission.%20We%20started%20out%20staring%20at%20each%20other%20around%20a%20kitchen%20table%2C%20wondering%20what%20research%20we%20should%20do.%20Back%20then%2C%20we%20did%20not%20contemplate%20products%2C%20a%20business%20model.%20We%20could%20not%20contemplate%20the%20direct%20benefits%20of%20AI%20being%20used%20for%20medical%20advice%2C%20learning%2C%20productivity%2C%20and%20much%20more%2C%20or%20the%20needs%20for%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20of%20compute%20to%20train%20models%20and%20serve%20users.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20did%20not%20really%20know%20how%20AGI%20was%20going%20to%20get%20built%2C%20or%20used.%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20could%20imagine%20an%20oracle%20that%20could%20tell%20scientists%20and%20presidents%20what%20to%20do%2C%20and%20although%20it%20could%20be%20incredibly%20dangerous%2C%20maybe%20those%20few%20people%20could%20be%20trusted%20with%20it.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20lot%20of%20people%20around%20OpenAI%20in%20the%20early%20days%20thought%20AI%20should%20only%20be%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20few%20trusted%20people%20who%20could%20%26quot%3Bhandle%20it%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20now%20see%20a%20way%20for%20AGI%20to%20directly%20empower%20everyone%20as%20the%20most%20capable%20tool%20in%20human%20history.%20If%20we%20can%20do%20this%2C%20we%20believe%20people%20will%20build%20incredible%20things%20for%20each%20other%20and%20continue%20to%20drive%20society%20and%20quality%20of%20life%20forward.%20It%20will%20of%20course%20not%20be%20all%20used%20for%20good%2C%20but%20we%20trust%20humanity%20and%20think%20the%20good%20will%20outweigh%20the%20bad%20by%20orders%20of%20magnitude.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20are%20committed%20to%20this%20path%20of%20democratic%20AI.%20We%20want%20to%20put%20incredible%20tools%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20everyone.%20We%20are%20amazed%20and%20delighted%20by%20what%20they%20are%20creating%20with%20our%20tools%2C%20and%20how%20much%20they%20want%20to%20use%20them.%20We%20want%20to%20open%20source%20very%20capable%20models.%20We%20want%20to%20give%20our%20users%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20freedom%20in%20how%20we%20let%20them%20use%20our%20tools%20within%20broad%20boundaries%2C%20even%20if%20we%20don't%20always%20share%20the%20same%20moral%20framework%2C%20and%20to%20let%20our%20users%20make%20decisions%20about%20the%20behavior%20of%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20believe%20this%20is%20the%20best%20path%20forward%E2%80%94AGI%20should%20enable%20all%20of%20humanity%20to%20benefit%20each%20other.%20We%20realize%20some%20people%20have%20very%20different%20opinions.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20want%20to%20build%20a%20brain%20for%20the%20world%20and%20make%20it%20super%20easy%20for%20people%20to%20use%20for%20whatever%20they%20want%20(subject%20to%20few%20restrictions%3B%20freedom%20shouldn't%20impinge%20on%20other%20people's%20freedom%2C%20for%20example).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPeople%20are%20using%20ChatGPT%20to%20increase%20their%20productivity%20as%20scientists%2C%20coders%2C%20and%20much%20more%E2%81%A0.%20People%20are%20using%20ChatGPT%20to%20solve%20serious%20healthcare%20challenges%20they%20are%20facing%20and%20learn%20more%20than%20ever%20before.%20People%20are%20using%20ChatGPT%20to%20get%20advice%20about%20how%20to%20handle%20difficult%20situations.%20We%20are%20very%20proud%20to%20offer%20a%20service%20that%20is%20doing%20so%20much%20for%20so%20many%20people%3B%20it%20is%20the%20one%20of%20most%20direct%20fulfillments%20of%20our%20mission%20we%20can%20imagine.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBut%20they%20want%20to%20use%20it%20much%20more%3B%20we%20currently%20cannot%20supply%20nearly%20as%20much%20AI%20as%20the%20world%20wants%20and%20we%20have%20to%20put%20usage%20limits%20on%20our%20systems%20and%20run%20them%20slowly.%20As%20the%20systems%20become%20more%20capable%2C%20they%20will%20want%20to%20use%20it%20even%20more%2C%20for%20even%20more%20wonderful%20things.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20had%20no%20idea%20this%20was%20going%20to%20be%20the%20state%20of%20the%20world%20when%20we%20launched%20our%20research%20lab%20almost%20a%20decade%20ago.%20But%20now%20that%20we%20see%20this%20picture%2C%20we%20are%20thrilled.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIt%20is%20time%20for%20us%20to%20evolve%20our%20structure.%20There%20are%20three%20things%20we%20want%20to%20accomplish%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20operate%20and%20get%20resources%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20we%20can%20make%20our%20services%20broadly%20available%20to%20all%20of%20humanity%2C%20which%20currently%20requires%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20and%20may%20eventually%20require%20trillions%20of%20dollars.%20We%20believe%20this%20is%20the%20best%20way%20for%20us%20to%20fulfill%20our%20mission%20and%20to%20get%20people%20to%20create%20massive%20benefits%20for%20each%20other%20with%20these%20new%20tools.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20want%20our%20nonprofit%20to%20be%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20effective%20nonprofit%20in%20history%20that%20will%20be%20focused%20on%20using%20AI%20to%20enable%20the%20highest-leverage%20outcomes%20for%20people.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3E%20We%20want%20to%20deliver%20beneficial%20AGI.%20This%20includes%20contributing%20to%20the%20shape%20of%20safety%20and%20alignment%3B%20we%20are%20proud%20of%20our%20track%20record%20with%20the%20systems%20we%20have%20launched%2C%20the%20alignment%20research%20we%20have%20done%2C%20processes%20like%20red%20teaming%2C%20and%20transparency%20into%20model%20behavior%20with%20innovations%20like%20the%20model%20spec%E2%81%A0.%20AI%20accelerates%2C%20our%20commitment%20to%20safety%20grows%20stronger.%20We%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20democratic%20AI%20wins%20over%20authoritarian%20AI.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20made%20the%20decision%20for%20the%20nonprofit%20to%20stay%20in%20control%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3Eafter%20hearing%20from%20civic%20leaders%20and%20having%20discussions%20with%20the%20offices%20of%20the%20Attorneys%20General%20of%20California%20and%20Delaware.%20We%20look%20forward%20to%20advancing%20the%20details%20of%20this%20plan%20in%20continued%20conversation%20with%20them%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20our%20newly%20appointed%20nonprofit%20commissioners.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOpenAI%20was%20founded%20as%20a%20nonprofit%2C%20is%20today%20a%20nonprofit%20that%20oversees%20and%20controls%20the%20for-profit%2C%20and%20going%20forward%20will%20remain%20a%20nonprofit%20that%20oversees%20and%20controls%20the%20for-profit.%20That%20will%20not%20change.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20for-profit%20LLC%20under%20the%20nonprofit%20will%20transition%20to%20a%20Public%20Benefit%20Corporation%20(PBC)%20with%20the%20same%20mission.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3EPBCs%20have%20become%20the%20standard%20for-profit%20structure%20for%20other%20AGI%20labs%20like%20Anthropic%20and%20X.ai%2C%20as%20well%20as%20many%20purpose%20driven%20companies%20like%20Patagonia.%20We%20think%20it%20makes%20sense%20for%20us%2C%20too.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EInstead%20of%20our%20current%20complex%20capped-profit%20structure%E2%80%94which%20made%20sense%20when%20it%20looked%20like%20there%20might%20be%20one%20dominant%20AGI%20effort%20but%20doesn't%20in%20a%20world%20of%20many%20great%20AGI%20companies%E2%80%94we%20are%20moving%20to%20a%20normal%20capital%20structure%20where%20everyone%20has%20stock.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20sale%2C%20but%20a%20change%20of%20structure%20to%20something%20simpler.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20nonprofit%20will%20continue%20to%20control%20the%20PBC%2C%20and%20will%20become%20a%20big%20shareholder%20in%20the%20PBC%2C%20in%20an%20amount%20supported%20by%20independent%20financial%20advisors%2C%20giving%20the%20nonprofit%20resources%20to%20support%20programs%20so%20AI%20can%20benefit%20many%20different%20communities%2C%20consistent%20with%20the%20mission.%20And%20as%20the%20PBC%20grows%2C%20the%20nonprofit's%20resources%20will%20grow%2C%20so%20it%20can%20do%20even%20more.%20We're%20excited%20to%20soon%20get%20recommendations%20from%20our%20nonprofit%20commission%20on%20how%20we%20can%20help%20make%20sure%20AI%20benefits%20everyone%E2%80%94not%20just%20a%20few.%20Their%20ideas%20will%20focus%20on%20how%20our%20nonprofit%20work%20can%20support%20a%20more%20democratic%20AI%20future%2C%20and%20have%20real%20impact%20in%20areas%20like%20health%2C%20education%2C%20public%20services%2C%20and%20scientific%20discovery.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20believe%20this%20sets%20us%20up%20to%20continue%20to%20make%20rapid%2C%20safe%20progress%20and%20to%20put%20great%20AI%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20everyone.%20Creating%20AGI%20is%20our%20brick%20in%20the%20path%20of%20human%20progress%3B%20we%20can't%20wait%20to%20see%20what%20bricks%20you%20will%20add%20next.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESam%20Altman%3Cbr%3EMay%202025%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-non-profit-control-public-benefit-corporation-sam-altman-letter-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746471056000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a7f1c0aab37011780b7666%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-non-profit-control-public-benefit-corporation-sam-altman-letter-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20published%20a%20letter%20announcing%20the%20plan%20on%20Monday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aaltchek%40insider.com%20(Ana%20Altchek)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-non-profit-control-public-benefit-corporation-sam-altman-letter-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20airport%E2%80%99s%20closed%20runway%20to%20open%20today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746471032000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-120909197%2Cimgsize-1066968.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fdelhi-airports-closed-runway-to-open-today%2Farticleshow%2F120909203.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Great%20news%20for%20air%20travelers%20as%20Delhi%20Airport's%20mai