0you've%20prepared%20for%20that%2C%20you've%20got%20some%20cash%20on%20the%20sidelines%2C%20you%20can%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20fear%2C%26quot%3B%20Crowell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20trick%20is%2C%20when%20there's%20nothing%20to%20do%2C%20do%20nothing%2C%26quot%3B%20Buffett%20once%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cb00ee02-e98e-4f5d-aefc-caa2c66dc655%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Make%20a%20plan%20and%20stick%20with%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20didn't%20get%20rich%20overnight%20%E2%80%94%20in%20fact%2C%2099%25%20of%20his%20wealth%20came%20after%20age%2050.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETime%2C%20discipline%2C%20and%20compound%20interest%20are%20all%20critical%20components%20to%20Buffett's%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20Buffett's%20investment%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-best-and-worst-investments-geico-apple-sees-candy-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECoca-Cola%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example.%20Between%201988%20and%201989%2C%20Buffett%20purchased%20%241.3%20billion%20of%20shares%20in%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGrowth%20occurred%20every%20year%2C%20just%20as%20certain%20as%20birthdays.%20All%20Charlie%20and%20I%20were%20required%20to%20do%20was%20cash%20Coke's%20dividend%20checks%2C%26quot%3B%20Buffett%20wrote%20in%20Berkshire%20Hathaway's%202022%20annual%20report.%20Berkshire%20Hathaway's%20stake%20in%20Coca-Cola%20is%20currently%20valued%20at%20over%20%2428%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it's%20not%20just%20about%20the%20stocks%20you%20buy.%20It's%20also%20about%20building%20up%20healthy%20financial%20habits%20such%20as%20avoiding%20high-interest%20debt%20on%20credit%20cards%20and%20investing%20regularly%20and%20early%20on%2C%20Buffett%20recommends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-career-lessons-berkshire-hathaway-succession-stocks-value-investing-2