%20Melissa%20Goldman%2C%20a%20partner%20and%20tech%20leader%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs.%20She%20started%20her%20career%2030%20years%20ago%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%20as%20an%20analyst%20and%20worked%20her%20way%20to%20managing%20director%20before%20departing%20for%20the%20rival%20firm%20JPMorgan%20Chase%2C%20where%20she%20helped%20lead%20the%20corporate%20tech%20division%20as%20a%20chief%20information%20officer.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EGoldman%20joined%20Google%20in%202022%20as%20a%20vice%20president%20and%20global%20head%20of%20corporate%20engineering%2C%20creating%20and%20deploying%20technologies%20that%20power%20Google's%20internal%20systems.%20Last%20fall%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-hires-googles-melissa-goldman-new-tech-head-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EGoldman%20returned%20to%20Goldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20where%20she%20runs%20the%20engineering%20teams%20powering%20the%20bank's%20investment%20banking%20and%20sales%20and%20trading%20units.%20This%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20New%20York%20City-based%20Goldman.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20a%20graduate%20of%20Carnegie%20Mellon%20University%20back%20in%20the%20early%201990s.%20The%20experience%20of%20being%20a%20computer%20science%20student%20at%20a%20very%20technical%20university%20meant%20you%20spent%20most%20of%20your%20time%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20engineering%20building%20doing%20your%20programming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20that%20the%20way%20I%20wanted%20to%20use%20my%20technology%20skills%20was%20really%20to%20apply%20them%20to%20real-world%20problems%2C%20where%20your%20technology%20would%20make%20a%20material%20difference%20toward%20a%20product%20or%20a%20business%2C%20where%20you%20could%20actually%20see%20the%20impact%20of%20your%20work%20in%20almost%20a%20real-time%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20ended%20up%20in%20financial%20services%2C%20I%20couldn't%20have%20been%20more%20pleased.%20The%20volumes%2C%20speed%2C%20and%20characteristics%20of%20what%20drives%20the%20business%20are%20tied%20to%20actually%20being%20able%20to%20build%20and%20engineer%20systems%20and%20solutions%20that%20enable%20all%20of%20that%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20responsibilities%20during%20my%20first%20stint%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%20was%20the%20collateral%20management%20system%2C%20which%20helped%20manage%20some%20of%20the%20contractual%20relationships%20with%20our%20counterparts.%20I%20was%20helping%20the%20firm%20manage%20risk%20and%20relationships%20with%20our%20clients.%20It%20was%20my%20responsibility%20to%20architect%20and%20build%20out%20a%20system%20that%20was%20nimble%20and%20could%20manage%20the%20complexities%20of%20these%20relationships%20and%20calculate%20money%20moving%20between%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%20more%20stories%20from%20BI's%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EPath%20to%20Wall%20Street%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0series%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinance-careers-investment-banking-private-equity-hedge-funds-articles-videos-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20what%20it's%20really%20like%20to%20work%20for%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-hedge-fund-career-multistrategy-portfolio-manager-churn-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3Ehedge%20fund%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20data%20showing%20where%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-bank-employee-demographic-front-office-education-race-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3Ethe%20average%20banker%20went%20to%20school%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20how%20much%20she%20makes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20responsibility%20became%20even%20more%20pronounced%20during%20times%20of%20volatility%2C%20and%20I%20was%20able%20to%20see%20firsthand%20how%20my%20work%20was%20pivotal%20in%20important%20times%20for%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20projects%20involved%20enabling%20a%20new%20financial%20product%20that%20we%20could%20offer%20to%20our%20clients%20or%20operating%20our%20businesses%20in%20additional%20countries%20around%20the%20world.%20Often%2C%20the%20work%20provides%20new%20and%20innovative%20ways%20to%20leverage%20our%20data%20to%20create%20greater%20insights%20and%20transparency%20into%20various%20decision-making%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20left%20finance%20for%20Google%20out%20of%20curiosity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20engineer%2C%20I%20was%20interested%20in%20having%20the%20opportunity%20to%20work%20in%20tech%20and%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20building%20of%20products.%20I%20had%20built%20a%20lot%20of%20expertise%20through%20my%20work%20in%20finance%20that%20was%20very%20applicable%20to%20the%20tech%20industry%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20could%20learn%20something%20new%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20a%20technology%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20I%20was%20focused%20on%20impacted%20the%20entire%20employee%20base%20of%20Google.%20We%20built%20and%20implemented%20the%20systems%20used%20by%20Googlers%20around%20the%20world%2C%20making%20sure%20people%20had%20what%20was%20needed%20to%20get%20their%20jobs%20done%20and%20the%20company%20had%20the%20systems%20in%20place%20to%20run%20it.%20So%2C%20my%20work%20had%20a%20direct%20impact%20on%20the%20employees%20of%20Google%20and%20an%20indirect%20impact%20on%20the%20customers%20of%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20missed%20this%20sense%20of%20purpose%20toward%20very%20tangible%20business%20results%20%E2%80%94the%20volatility%2C%20the%20constant%20need%20to%20be%20nimble%2C%20responsive%2C%20and%20reactive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArguably%2C%20I%20couldn't%20put%20that%20same%20kind%20of%20art%20and%20finesse%20to%20work%20at%20Google%20in%20the%20way%20that%20I%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20within%20financial%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20is%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20remind%20folks%20of%20this%20when%20they%20try%20to%20make%20the%20comparison%20%E2%80%94%20that%20tech%20and%20finance%20have%20a%20different%20set%20of%20products%20and%20a%20different%20environment.%20Financial%20services%20is%20an%20industry%20where%20tech%20is%20a%20differentiator%20to%20the%20success%20of%20the%20business%3B%20at%20a%20company%20like%20Google%2C%20tech%20is%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ed5f432-3d9d-412a-a98c-f3d70f634b74%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20handle%20the%20rate%20of%20change%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20thrilled%20to%20be%20here.%20But%20it's%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pace%20and%20rate%20of%20change%20are%20exceptional.%20How%20technology%20is%20evolving%2C%20the%20opportunities%20to%20bring%20AI%20and%20automation%20and%20different%20kinds%20of%20efficiency%20elements%20to%20what%20we%20do%20and%20how%20we%20do%20it%20(every%20couple%20of%20weeks%20there's%20something%20new%20and%20different)%2C%20how%20we%20challenge%20ourselves%20to%20be%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20these%20things%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20exhausting%2C%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20amazing%20time%20to%20be%20an%20engineer%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20lot%20of%20responsibility%20to%20do%20it%20well%20and%20stay%20nimble%20enough%20to%20respond%20and%20react%20to%20the%20changes%20that%20are%20out%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20question%20AI%20will%20be%20a%20material%20part%20of%20our%20journey%20for%20the%20next%20decades%2C%20and%20for%20someone%20like%20me%2C%20it%20will%20involve%20being%20on%20the%20front%20lines%20of%20maximizing%20the%20technology%20to%20help%20our%20people%20better%20serve%20our%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlready%2C%20we%20are%20seeing%20a%20roughly%2020%25%20increase%20in%20efficiency%20depending%20on%20the%20developer%20and%20the%20use%20case.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20impactful%20ways%20we%20can%20use%20it%20is%20to%20take%20the%20toil%20out%20of%20the%20tasks%20that%20we%20would%20rather%20not%20have%20our%20best%20and%20brightest%20minds%20working%20on%20and%20instead%20have%20them%20work%20on%20designing%20new%20products.%20We're%20going%20to%20ask%20some%20individuals%20on%20our%20teams%20to%20do%20different%20things%2C%20but%20it's%20more%20about%20evolving%20their%20role%20than%20a%20flat-out%20completely%20different%20way%20of%20operating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20believe%20engineers%20will%20maintain%20their%20creative%20role%20in%20designing%20systems%20and%20architectures.%20As%20technology%20evolves%2C%20they%20will%20still%20act%20as%20the%20conductor%20in%20an%20orchestra%20of%20additional%20instruments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20we're%20only%20scratching%20the%20surface%20of%20what%20opportunities%20we'll%20be%20able%20to%20realize%20through%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWant%20to%20share%20your%20career%20path%20with%20us%3F%20Fill%20out%20this%20quick%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSe9A5QqsX-JIQmtT-1H4IM6UuS5c4Z47_31sWPhjnsqhen8eQ%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dheader%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Eform%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-wall-street-finance-goldman-sachs-google-jpmorgan-career-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746465912000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681239d1c6ad288d147f8ded%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-wall-street-finance-goldman-sachs-google-jpmorgan-career-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Melissa%20Goldman%20returned%20to%20Wall%20Street%20after%20stints%20at%20Go