change%2C%20but%20how%20fast%20we%20can%20begin.%20One%20Kolkata-based%20company%20is%20stepping%20up%20to%20bring%20about%20that%20change.%20Pepcom%20Private%20Limited%20is%20replacing%20single-use%20plastic%20with%20eco-friendly%2C%20paper-based%20packaging%20that%20is%20just%20as%20effective%20but%20far%20safer%20for%20both%20the%20environment%20and%20the%20food%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20solve%20a%20problem%20that%20affects%20both%20the%20environment%20and%20human%20health.%20Plastic%20packaging%20is%20harmful%2C%20but%20the%20food%20industry%20needs%20practical%20solutions.%20We%20needed%20to%20create%20something%20that%20worked%20and%20was%20safe%2C%20sustainable%2C%20and%20effective%20for%20the%20industry%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sagnik%20Mukherjee%20(38)%2C%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20founder%20and%20CEO.%20Sanjoy%20Banerjee%2C%20a%20close%20neighbour%20and%20long-time%20friend%2C%20also%20decided%20to%20join%20hands%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20boardrooms%20to%20green%20dreams%3A%20How%20two%20professionals%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20step%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20starting%20their%20packaging%20startup%2C%20the%20co-founders%20had%20spent%20decades%20in%20different%20corporate%20roles.%20Sagnik%20worked%20at%20Mahindra%20Automotive%20Sales%20%26amp%3B%20Service%20for%20around%2017%20years%2C%20while%20Sanjoy%20was%20at%20Hero%20MotoCorp.%20Even%20though%20they%20were%20successful%20in%20their%20respective%20careers%2C%20they%20were%20always%20deeply%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352011%2Fnikhil-kumar-chintan-prajapati-greenevo-bio-bottles-plastic-free-sugarcane-biodegradable%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econcerned%20about%20the%20environment%3C%2Fa%3E.%20During%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20quit%20their%20jobs%20and%20pursue%20a%20venture%20aligned%20with%20their%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201500px)%20100vw%2C%201500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-23-at-12.31.42-1-1-1746454851.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pepcom%20India%20was%20launched%20in%202022%2C%20and%20the%20sales%20began%20in%20September%202023%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-23-at-12.31.42-1-1-1746454851.jpeg%201500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-23-at-12.31.42-1-1-1746454851-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-23-at-12.31.42-1-1-1746454851-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-23-at-12.31.42-1-1-1746454851-768x432.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-23-at-12.31.42-1-1-1746454851-1200x675.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-23-at-12.31.42-1-1-1746454851-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-425168%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22844%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPepcom%20India%20was%20launched%20in%202022%2C%20and%20the%20sales%20began%20in%20September%202023%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20pandemic%2C%20we%20saw%20a%20huge%20rise%20in%20demand%20for%20sustainable%20alternatives%2C%20especially%20in%20food%20packaging%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sagnik%20tells%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20there%20weren%E2%80%99t%20many%20practical%20solutions%20available%2C%20and%20we%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20to%20step%20in%20and%20make%20a%20real%20impact.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20in%202022%2C%20Pepcom%20India%20was%20born%2C%20an%20eco-friendly%20packaging%20company%20determined%20to%20offer%20a%20viable%20alternative%20to%20plastic%20in%20the%20food%20industry.%20The%20company%20began%20sales%20in%20September%202023%20after%20studying%20the%20market%20thoroughly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fimage-5-1_11zon-1746455233-500x461.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20food%20industry%20plays%20a%20huge%20part%20in%20aggravating%20the%20plastic%20problem%2C%20and%20Pepcom%20India%20decided%20to%20solve%20it%20by%20providing%20a%20suitable%20alternative%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fimage-5-1_11zon-1746455233-500x461.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fimage-5-1_11zon-1746455233-300x277.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fimage-5-1_11zon-1746455233-150x138.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fimage-5-1_11zon-1746455233.jpg%20553w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-425175%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22461%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20food%20indus