%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20researching%20suppliers%20before%20we%20found%20ITC%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sagnik%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20paper%20is%20perfect%20for%20our%20needs%20and%20can%20contain%20hot%20food%2C%20in%20its%20exact%20composition%2C%20for%20long%20hours.%20That%20was%20important%20for%20us%20from%20the%20very%20beginning.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20paperboard%20arrives%2C%20the%20process%20of%20turning%20it%20into%20packaging%20begins.%20The%20first%20step%20is%20printing%20the%20containers%20with%20food-safe%20inks%2C%20making%20sure%20that%20each%20product%20meets%20health%20and%20safety%20standards.%20This%20is%20done%20using%20a%20printing%20press%2C%20which%20applies%20logos%20and%20branding%20where%20needed%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20punching%20process.%20The%20paperboard%20is%20then%20fed%20into%20a%20machine%2C%20which%20carefully%20shapes%20the%20paper%20into%20the%20desired%20form.%20Whether%20it%20is%20a%20bowl%20or%20a%20lid%2C%20each%20piece%20is%20precisely%20cut%20and%20made%20ready%20for%20folding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20it%20goes%20through%20a%20folder-gluer%20machine%2C%20which%20folds%20and%20seals%20the%20containers%20into%20their%20final%20form.%20The%20process%20guarantees%20that%20each%20container%20is%20sturdy%20enough%20to%20handle%20hot%2C%20greasy%2C%20or%20wet%20food%20without%20falling%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20547px)%20100vw%2C%20547px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fimage-2-1_11zon-1746455338.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22547%5C%22%20alt%3D%5