mbitious%20journey%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20not%20just%20intrigued%20by%20batteries.%20I%20was%20obsessed%20with%20the%20time%20gap%20between%20testing%20and%20diagnosis.%20Existing%20battery%20testing%20methods%20were%20slow%2C%20clunky%2C%20and%20offered%20very%20little%20insight.%20I%20believed%20we%20could%20compress%20hours%20of%20testing%20into%20minutes%2C%20and%20make%20the%20results%20comprehensive%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Ajay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETwo%20engineers%20fixing%20the%20EV%20puzzle%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETogether%2C%20they%20began%20working%20on%20a%20tool%20that%20can%20analyse%20battery%20health%20faster%2C%20more%20accurately%2C%20and%20without%20the%20need%20for%20expensive%20and%20imported%20machinery.%20What%20followed%20was%20a%20year%20of%20intense%20research%20and%20development%2C%20from%20reading%20through%20research%20papers%20and%20patents%20to%20building%20prototypes%20with%20open-source%20kits.%20They%20consulted%20with%20battery%20experts%2C%20attended%20international%20conferences%2C%20and%20conducted%20experiments%20in%20university%20labs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20mid-2021%2C%20the%20duo%20launched%20BatteryOk%20Technologies.%20And%20on%2015%20August%202022%2C%20they%20officially%20introduced%20EV%20Doctor%20to%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20