D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20like%20a%20full%20body%20check-up%2C%20but%20for%20batteries.%20It%20does%20not%20just%20show%20if%20something%20is%20wrong%2C%20it%20gives%20clarity%20on%20health%2C%20safety%2C%20and%20potential%20risks.%20That%20allows%20us%20to%20take%20preventive%20steps%20before%20anything%20serious%20happens.%20By%20using%20EV%20Doctor%2C%20I%20have%20tested%20hundreds%20of%20batteries%2C%20and%20not%20a%20single%20one%20has%20led%20to%20thermal%20issues.%20That%20alone%20has%20probably%20saved%20us%20lakhs%20in%20potential%20damage%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20workshop%20owner%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T215635.602_11zon-1746030410.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20duo%20has%20sold%20600%20units%20of%20the%20EV%20Doctor%20so%20far%20in%202025%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T215635.602_11zon-1746030410.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T215635.602_11zon-1746030410-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T215635.602_11zon-1746030410-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T215635.602_11zon-1746030410-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T215635.602_11zon-174603