s%20also%20the%20science%20behind%20its%20safety.%20Working%20with%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20Gandhinagar%20(IIT-GN)%2C%20the%20team%20conducted%20over%2060%20thermal%20runaway%20tests%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20device%20can%20reliably%20detect%20potential%20fire%20hazards%20in%20battery%20cells.%20These%20tests%20also%20informed%20the%20device%E2%80%99s%20safety%20prediction%20algorithms%2C%20which%20continue%20to%20evolve%20with%20every%20battery%20scanned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20consciously%20reduced%20the%20size%20from%201%20kilogram%20to%20300%20grams%20to%20make%20it%20portable%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ajay%20says.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20real%20innovation%20is%20in%20how%20much%20it%20can%20do%20in%20so%20little%20time%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20existing%20devices.%20It%20can%20help%20EV%20owners%20get%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20all%20the%20aspects%20of%20the%20battery.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20calibrated%20the%20device%20against%20international%20benchmarks%20such%20as%20the%20International%20Electrotechnical%20Commission%20(IEC)%20and%20Underwriters%20Laboratories%20(UL)%20standards%2C%20guaranteeing%20it%20meets%20global%20expectations.%20It%20is%20now%20part%20of%20the%20curriculum%20at%20IIT-GN%2C%20where%20students%20learn%20battery%20safety%20and%20diagnostics%20using%20the%20device%20in%20hands-on%20lab%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T220532.777_11zon-1746030958.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20client%20list%20for%20the%20EV%20Doctor%20includes%20MG%20Motors%2C%20Zypp%20Electric%2C%20Yulu%2C%20White%20Carbon%2C%20%20and%20Jitendra%20EV%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.co